Calculate monthly costs¶

The plot below represents one month. The X-axis is time, Y-axis is active users. Each step represents on hour of time, and weekends are shaded in grey.

Draw the usage pattern below, then click the button and you’ll get an estimated monthly cost for your JupyterHub deployment.
